### Obtener todos los partners
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/partners HTTP/1.1

### Obtener un partner por id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/partners/1a2b3c4d-0001 HTTP/1.1

### Crear un Partner con POST
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/partners HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json 

{
  "name": "win"
}

### Actualizar un Partner con PATCH
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/partners/1a2b3c4d-0001 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "win2",
  "active": false
}
